    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist-spec performance machine featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and its signature individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct mechanical connection to the M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe inspection, addressing the primary concerns for this chassis. The hydraulic steering remains sharp, and the naturally aspirated power delivery is flawless up to the 8,400 RPM redline. This is a mechanically robust example optimized for spirited driving and technical engagement.",
