    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This meticulously cared-for sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep gloss, with only minor, expected road wear consistent with careful highway driving and garage storage. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while all digital displays and electronic features remain crisp and fully functional. Mechanically, this vehicle has been maintained with a proactive approach, featuring a complete service log, a recently serviced cooling system, and high-quality tires with ample tread life remaining. It shifts smoothly through all gears, idles quietly, and provides a composed, rattle-free ride. This is an honest, well-sorted vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
