      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! Honestly, this ride has been so good to me\u2014it's super reliable and still looks great pulling into the driveway. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in solid shape, perfect for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. It runs like a dream and is ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
