    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This A80 Supra Turbo is a prime example of over-engineered Japanese performance. Powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, the sequential twin-turbocharger system provides a linear power band and exceptional reliability. The drivetrain features the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery to the rear wheels. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, and the four-piston front calipers offer consistent stopping power. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-maintained driver, the mechanical vitals are robust, with no signs of boost leaks or synchro grind. It is a highly capable, driver-focused platform for any enthusiast.",
